<section id="about" class="section bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <h2 class="text-primary">關於 Forest Calm</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Forest Calm 相信，真正的守護，始於對生命最純粹的尊重。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          因此，我們以天然 × 舒敏 × 安心為品牌的核心信念，堅持只選用溫和純淨的植物成分，為敏感毛孩量身打造每一瓶洗護產品。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          天然，是回歸初心，拒絕多餘添加，只保留大自然最純粹的溫柔。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          舒敏，是理解脆弱肌膚的需要，用溫和成分撫平每一寸不適。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          安心，是每一次洗澡都像在森林中沐浴，讓毛孩感受無負擔的陪伴。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          我們深知，對毛孩來說，清潔不只是儀式，更是一場療癒的對話。<br>
          Forest Calm，願成為你與毛孩之間，最溫柔、最純粹的連結。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8 italic">
          Gentle as a forest. Pure as your love.<br>
          用自然的方式，守護每一份真摯的愛。
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="bg-primary-light text-white rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">自然舒緩</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">使用燕麥、蘆薈、洋甘菊等天然成分</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="bg-primary-light text-white rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">無添加香精</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">避免刺激成分，提供無香或天然香氛版本</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="bg-primary-light text-white rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">在地製造</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">台灣研發生產，品質透明可信</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="lg:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src="/image/about.png" 
            alt="Dog enjoying bath time" 
            class="rounded-xl shadow-xl w-full object-cover"
            width="800"
            height="600"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Decorative elements -->
  <div class="absolute -left-24 -bottom-24 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/10 rounded-full"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-20 right-0 w-32 h-64 bg-secondary/10 rounded-l-full"></div>
</section>